'''[[List of Augment Modules|Augment Modules]]''' are items similar to Auxiliaries that can provide special skills if equipping a +10 T2 version, as well as upgrade unique ship skills for specific ships with their unique augments. Unlike regular gear improved and crafted by blueprints and parts (see [[Equipment#Upgrade_(Enhance)|here]]), Augmentation uses a special system involving stones to create and upgrade your Augment Modules.

Augment Modules can only be equipped by ships with are fully Limit Broken, excluding META ships, Research ships, UR ships, and Bulins which can use them at any moment.

