===Slash Reload===
All slash attacks are based on the ''Lead Vanguard Ship''. Once the Lead Vanguard Ship takes damage, a slash is fired. There is a '''15s''' cooldown between slashes (starts on cooldown). '''5s''' after the cooldown ends, if the Lead Vanguard Ship hasn't taken damage, a slash is fired.<br/>

===Slash Damage=== 
Slash Attacks are assigned a '''Level''', which is dependent on the number and type of Slash Attack Augment Module(s) equipped. When different types of slashes are used in the same fleet, both activate at their respective levels. <br/>

'''Examples''':
* [[Hammer]] + [[Hammer]] + [[Sword]] = '''Level 3''' Slash Attack - Spread.
* [[Hammer]] + [[Dual Swords]] + [[Greatsword]] = '''Level 1''' Slash Attack - Spread + '''Level 2''' Slash Attack - Area

All Slash Attacks are unaffected by enemy Armor Modifiers, and work in all game content (including [[Exercise]]).
